sql:
SELECT DISTINCT s.name
FROM staff s
JOIN conference_participation cp_speaker ON s.staff_ID = cp_speaker.staff_ID AND cp_speaker.role = 'speaker'
JOIN conference_participation cp_sponsor ON s.staff_ID = cp_sponsor.staff_ID AND cp_sponsor.role = 'sponsor'
WHERE cp_speaker.Conference_ID = cp_sponsor.Conference_ID;
question: Show all staff names who have been both speaker and sponsor in some conference.

sql:
SELECT DISTINCT s1.name
FROM conference_participation cp1
JOIN conference_participation cp2 ON cp1.staff_ID = cp2.staff_ID AND cp1.Conference_ID = cp2.Conference_ID
JOIN staff s1 ON cp1.staff_ID = s1.staff_ID
WHERE cp1.role = 'speaker' AND cp2.role = 'sponsor'
question: Show all staff names who have been both speaker and sponsor in some conference.

sql:
SELECT DISTINCT s.name
FROM staff s
JOIN conference_participation cp1 ON s.staff_ID = cp1.staff_ID AND cp1.role = 'speaker'
JOIN conference_participation cp2 ON s.staff_ID = cp2.staff_ID AND cp2.role = 'sponsor' AND cp1.Conference_ID = cp2.Conference_ID;
question: Show all staff names who have been both speaker and sponsor in some conference.
